originalText.text: Rude staff, charged me over the price I was told upon coming in before 6am. Would never recommend or come back here. I’ve never been charged as much as $71 for the whole day!

originalText.text: The lot attendant is abrasive and rude. Turns me away when he feels like it and not according to the lot being full. I work until 11:30pm I made a reservation that allows me to leave at 12 am. He says he closes at 11:45pm. Today he tried to charge me an oversized car fee for the first time since I been parking there. At first he said $15 and I refused so he said his boss would charge me $6. I left the lot and I will follow up with his boss. It’s always an unpleasant experience but this lot is the most affordable near my job. I drive a Lexus 2002 rx 300.
